source: TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_000<tab>Nothing seems particularly suspicious here. Maybe you'll have better luck at another location.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_000<tab>特に怪しいところはなさそうだ……。
別の場所を調査してみよう。

source: TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_005<tab>You hear the chittering of an animal reverberating beyond the rock wall. Perhaps it signifies a secret cavern? Regardless, the felicitous furball will want to know of your findings.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_005<tab>どうやら、内部が空洞になっているようだ！
「ねこみみさん」に、調査結果を報告しよう。

source: TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_010<tab>Nothing seems particularly suspicious here. Maybe you'll have better luck at another location.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_010<tab>特に怪しいところはなさそうだ……。
別の場所を調査してみよう。

source: TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_015<tab>Rapping your knuckles against the rock wall yields a hollow sound. Perhaps a secret cavern lies beyond? The determined digger will undoubtedly wish to hear of this.
target:
TEXT_CTSMJICAVESURVEY_00831_POINT_001_015<tab>どうやら中が空洞になっているようだ！
「たんけんくん」に、調査結果を報告しよう。
